{"tid":1931490,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[EFT] 逃離塔科夫- Escpe From Tarkov 薯叔教室 EP.2 賺錢篇","createTime":"2020-03-18T07:40:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-09T13:24:39.000Z","uid":240313,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ec5a71dad0120bd23bbf73f9208c438a7c73fded","tid":1931490,"uid":240313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T07:40:34.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RmQo8Wt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRmQo8Wt.jpg&h=fbfb044c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[EFT] 逃離塔科夫- Escpe From Tarkov  薯叔教室 EP.2</div><br />\n<br />\n            <div style=\"text-align: center;\">          <div style=\"text-align: center;\"></div>   <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">第貳章</span></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n多謝大家支持，Tarkov 群已經去到接近200人，我係度感謝各位既支持，望大家能係群入面享受Tarkov 既樂趣。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n回到正題，如果你係新手岩岩入坑買Standard Edition 既話，你有起始資金 三十萬，三十萬你會用黎做乜？<br />\n<br />\n買套裝入場 殺PMC 拎裝？ 升Hideout?  請大佬帶你去陰PMC?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SaQc2jE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSaQc2jE.jpg&h=776f2aa9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實以上皆可，但係由於呢個 0.12.4呢個patch 既更新，眾新手們要升到 10lv 先可以 進入Flea market,所以你地暫時只可以用 trading 商人入面既&quot;神兵&quot;......   即係你有錢都唔可以買到裝，呢個時候可以做咩呢？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. 入Factory 打Scav (強烈建議）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2xK1VFR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2xK1VFR.jpg&h=59656433&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n0lv&gt;10lv 大約要45000經驗值左右<br />\n<br />\n如果以一場大約2000經驗左右， 25場左右就可以升到上 10lv 開啟黑市之路<br />\n<br />\n你可能會問我又無裝  又無人帶 去打Factory 同送裝 有咩分別啊！！ <br />\n<br />\n無錯，你裝未必夠人好，但係Factory  係一個練習 CQB同心理質素既好地方<br />\n<br />\n首先, 我知我與你會愛得激烈, 愈親愈熱, 然後<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">短兵相接</span></span><br />\n<br />\n工廠環境窄, 主要係通道上開戰, 你可以用平民武器 (AK, PP-91, ADAR) 隨時殺左人, 可以搜掠資源&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt; 但你LOOT一條屍唔好照過10秒, 一照過秒, 隨時眼前一黑得不償失。<br />\n<br />\n心理質素好既玩家同心理質素唔夠強既玩家分別<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J9BLDki.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ9BLDki.png&h=bd88d71f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BpYFsdD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBpYFsdD.png&h=1c09620b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n姜大偉先生講過 :「再鋒利既刀都有生鏽,更何況係人」  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qRB7RGF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqRB7RGF.jpg&h=7ee1e0f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果你係打算一世都靠大佬同你打, 你大可以SKIP左我方案一, 直接跳去方案二。<br />\n<br />\n2. 跑刀流<br />\n<br />\n咩係跑刀? 跑刀係呢隻遊戲無成本,但又可以賺錢既一種手法<br />\n<br />\n方法就係唔著任何裝備, 求其入一個地圖, 之後將所得到既貴重物品 放曬入去Container (保險箱)入面, 即使死左都可以帶返出黎, 再變賣出去。<br />\n<br />\n我強烈建議新手們, 跑熟一個圖先, 薯叔係度建議大家跑熟 Reserve  (儲備站)<br />\n點解會提議大家先跑熟Reserve, 首先Reserve 地理環境, 俾大家好多藏身既地方<br />\n空地面積較小, 房屋多, 物資同資料豐富 , 雖然大家話怕俾SCAV殺, 但呢個真係講彩數<br />\n薯叔試過十次跑刀, 有4次都可以拎住戰利品, 仲要徹離埋 XD<br />\n<br />\nReserve 推介你去既點係 : <span style=\"color: red;\">顯卡房</span><br />\n其實呢幢樓,除左顯卡房外,成幢樓都係寶物庫, 但唔該...見到薯叔可唔可以唔殺呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n位置: 飛機頭對住幢樓既二樓 ,可以由2分45秒開始睇<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=r1rSMYfjsNw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dr1rSMYfjsNw&d=V4yVQ1MiaEIlcmjbsyBqFzizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=638b02de\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=r1rSMYfjsNw</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其他跑刀既細節就大家慢慢去感受, 但薯叔真係建議玩呢隻遊戲 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好純跑刀</span></span>!!!!!!<br />\n<br />\n你賺錢黎係為乜先!!! 「萬般帶不走,唯有業隨身」 呢隻係一隻射擊遊戲, 你可唔可以拎起你支槍, 出去同人打架,對下槍呀!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nMan is up!!!!!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 殺人越貨<br />\n<br />\n我比較建議呢個方案的話, 大家最好係組隊, 有個照應, 薯叔有個朋友岩岩玩呢隻遊戲個時, 俾人殺個時, 嚇到成個彈起左, 笑到我肚痛差D入ICU<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n殺人越貨可以培養到你對遊戲既熟悉度同埋隨時 PAK 死一個大佬 你會拎到豐厚既獎金獎品!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係初期一定會  死  死 死 同埋死!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但當你死到咁上下, 你開始有經驗, 你會入去DORM, 你會開始帶頭, 五人小隊分配好自己既工作, <br />\n死左既話幫隊友&quot;執屍&quot; , 成功一隊人帶返戰利品出黎, 你會有無比既滿足感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點先?! 睇先上面既文章會唔會激發起你小小入返隻Game既意慾先? Gear up! <br />\n帶上耳機,一齊再進入Tarkov 世界啦!!!!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n___________________________________________________________________________<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><br />\n薯叔, 年過三十, 鐘意打機, 但FPS 苦手, 反應隨年齡愈來愈慢, 但係仍然喜歡打機。<br />\n自問唔係一個射擊遊戲能手, 但係如果你地有興趣想知多D呢隻遊戲, 又或者入坑既可以隨時問我, 我知道既一定會答你地,祝大家成功逃離塔科夫。</span><br />\n<br />\nTwitch: <a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/hcp999\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Fhcp999&d=V4yVQ1MiaEIlcmjbsyBqFzizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=3e91f619\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.twitch.tv/hcp999</a><br />\nDiscord: <a href=\"https://discord.gg/aZDU2mG\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscord.gg%2FaZDU2mG&d=V4yVQ1MiaEIlcmjbsyBqFzizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=be241755\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://discord.gg/aZDU2mG</a>"},{"pid":"c55350f1d2a3f4ae8ca38d940b20dde12c1c94de","tid":1931490,"uid":161382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T08:20:51.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4850adc008d2121dc826186e2d35fb41d8e2cf91","tid":1931490,"uid":154505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T18:12:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe4a91eb85ebfc904b889a0c4e13c6c0b4475c87","tid":1931490,"uid":240313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T07:23:33.000Z","msg":"係超人?? 係雀仔?? 係薯叔呀!!!<br />\n薯叔台 今晚9點約實你<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/hcp999\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Fhcp999&d=V4yVQ1MiaEIlcmjbsyBqFzizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=3e91f619\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.twitch.tv/hcp999</a>"},{"pid":"190e6284a0b3f059200fc49c9cd74cb1d6f3fdf1","tid":1931490,"uid":36994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T10:19:00.000Z","msg":"薯叔好波"},{"pid":"332787e8f77f99b8e69cad0c2a2c1063818dda18","tid":1931490,"uid":83030,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T12:16:02.000Z","msg":"一覺得會洗白就唔想繼續玩落去<br />\n浪費時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96eca